  "instructions": "<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušaj audio snimak i odgovori na pitanje koje je navedeno ispod.</p>\n</section>",
  "explanation": "<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Vitenzi vya phrasal ni vitenzi vinavyounganishwa na viunganishi au vitenzi vidogo vinavyounda maana mpya. Katika sehemu hii ya mazungumzo, unaona tofauti kati ya <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to send something</span> na <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to send something over</span>.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">To send something</span> inamaanisha kuhamisha kitu kutoka mahali au mtu mmoja kwenda mwingine, wakati <span class=\"highlighted-text\">to send something over</span> inaongeza wazo la kuwasilisha kwa mtu au mahali, mara nyingi kwa njia isiyo rasmi au kidijitali. Angalia mfano mmoja wa kila moja:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">I'll send the letter tomorrow.</span> - Kauli ya msingi ya kuhamisha kitu.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Can you send over the file by email?</span> - Ovo naglašava slanje nečega <em>osobi</em>, obično na kratku udaljenost ili digitalno. Dodavanje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">over</span> čini ovaj izraz uobičajenijim u svakodnevnim razgovorima.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>",
